description:
Origin

Mom Spaceknight is a housewife, living in Warren, Michigan with her husband and daughter. She is forced to defend the space vampire race called Glarkians. The Glarkians threaten to harm her daughter Emma if she does not defend them.

Powers & Abilities

Mom Spaceknight uses an armor which can't be harmed by Anti-Zarian metals, such as the Vampblades.
name: Mom Spaceknight

deck: Calypso was a normal man and went by another name. He nearly died from a car crash that killed his wife and daughter, but his face was scared from burns and he has become devastated. After the crash, he made a deal with the devil/Minion to come back in exchange for souls. He harvests these souls by way of the Twisted Metal, a vehicular combat tournament where contestants rig up elaborate weapons systems to their cars to eliminate each other, with the last man standing being granted one wish from Calypso.
name: Calypso
